premise_source_doc_sentence: Stephanie Sengupta  (  also written as Stephanie SenGupta and Stéphanie Sengupta  )  is an American television producer and writer .

She is a co-creator of the series Reign and known for writing and co-producing episodes of the police procedural dramas Hawaii Five-0 , Law & Order and Law & Order : Criminal Intent , and for foreign adaptations of the Law & Order franchise .
She is of mixed Bengali Indian and French-American descent .
Her father is from Kolkata , West Bengal , India , while her mother is American , with French ancestry .
